Package: VirusSimulationR
Title: Interactive group simulation activity for viral spread in R.
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Melissa",
           family = "Ko",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mesako@stanford.edu")
Description: Shiny application that pulls data from a Google sheet populated by student-submitted responses from an in-class viral spread simulation activity. Application establishes connection to Google and starting number assignments using the configuration app, while the main app loads the data and provides a GUI for generating visualizations.
